### Where have all the men gone? Temporary Migration & Rural Public Works - A Discontinuity Approach

**Kasturi Kandalam** 

This paper examines the impact of India's rural employment guarantee scheme (MGNREGA) on temporary male migration using a regression discontinuity design. Exploiting discontinuities in program implementation, I analyze how public works employment affects migration decisions in rural households.

**Keywords**: Migration, MGNREGA, Public Works, Rural Development, India

