### From Charminar to Cyberabad: Political Economy of Software Industry in Erstwhile Unified Andhra Pradesh

**Kasturi Kandalam**

This study investigates the political economy factors that transformed Hyderabad from a traditional city into a major global IT hub. I examine the role of state policies, political leadership, and institutional changes in facilitating the emergence and growth of the software industry in Andhra Pradesh.

**Keywords**: Software Industry, Political Economy, Andhra Pradesh, Hyderabad, Regional Development, India

